{
  "video_id": "xVzkOWxd7uQ",
  "title": "Jeff Bezos On Breaking Up And Regulating Amazon",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 1790.0,
      "text": "Your most prominent critic at the moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1790.0,
      "end_time": 3373.0,
      "text": "is the president of the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 3373.0,
      "end_time": 6260.0,
      "text": "People are even saying that he may be willing"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6260.0,
      "end_time": 9670.0,
      "text": "to prepare initiatives to break up Amazon"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9670.0,
      "end_time": 11710.0,
      "text": "because it's too big, it's too successful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11710.0,
      "end_time": 13390.0,
      "text": "it's too dominant in too many sectors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 13390.0,
      "end_time": 15160.0,
      "text": "or for varied other reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 15160.0,
      "end_time": 17630.0,
      "text": "First of all, is this scenario of a break up something"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 17630.0,
      "end_time": 22610.0,
      "text": "that you take seriously, or you think it's just a fantasy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 22610.0,
      "end_time": 25550.0,
      "text": "- For me, again this is one those things where"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 25550.0,
      "end_time": 29190.0,
      "text": "you know, I focus on, and ask our teams"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 29190.0,
      "end_time": 31310.0,
      "text": "to focus on what we can control."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 31310.0,
      "end_time": 35187.0,
      "text": "And, I expect, whether it's the current US administration"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 35187.0,
      "end_time": 38629.0,
      "text": "or any other government agency anywhere in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 38629.0,
      "end_time": 42890.0,
      "text": "Amazon is now a large corporation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 42890.0,
      "end_time": 45530.0,
      "text": "and I expect us to be scrutinized."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45530.0,
      "end_time": 46690.0,
      "text": "We should be scrutinized."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 46690.0,
      "end_time": 50742.0,
      "text": "I think all large institutions should be scrutinized"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 50742.0,
      "end_time": 52140.0,
      "text": "and examined."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 52140.0,
      "end_time": 53840.0,
      "text": "It's reasonable."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 53840.0,
      "end_time": 56958.0,
      "text": "And, what's, you know, one thing to note about us"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 56960.0,
      "end_time": 63460.0,
      "text": "is that we have, we have gotten big in absolute terms"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 63820.0,
      "end_time": 66180.0,
      "text": "only very recently, so we've always been growing fast"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66180.0,
      "end_time": 71180.0,
      "text": "in percentage terms, but in 2010, just eight years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72590.0,
      "end_time": 75300.0,
      "text": "we had 30,000 employees."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75300.0,
      "end_time": 78730.0,
      "text": "So, in the last eight years we've gone from 30,000 employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78730.0,
      "end_time": 80750.0,
      "text": "to 560,000 employees."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80750.0,
      "end_time": 85700.0,
      "text": "So for us, you know, in my mind, I'm still delivering"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85700.0,
      "end_time": 87600.0,
      "text": "the packages to the post office myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87600.0,
      "end_time": 88649.0,
      "text": "You see what I'm saying?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 88650.0,
      "end_time": 93700.0,
      "text": "I still have all the memories of, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93700.0,
      "end_time": 95800.0,
      "text": "hoping one day we could afford a forklift."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95800.0,
      "end_time": 99820.0,
      "text": "And, obviously that's, my intellectual brain knows"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 99820.0,
      "end_time": 101289.0,
      "text": "that's just not the case anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101290.0,
      "end_time": 104610.0,
      "text": "We have 560,000 employees all over the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 104610.0,
      "end_time": 108580.0,
      "text": "and I know we should be scrutinized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108580.0,
      "end_time": 111800.0,
      "text": "and I think it's true, a big government institution"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 111800.0,
      "end_time": 113750.0,
      "text": "should be scrutinized, a big non profit institution"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113750.0,
      "end_time": 115920.0,
      "text": "should be scrutinized, big universities should"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115920.0,
      "end_time": 117803.0,
      "text": "be scrutinized, it just makes sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 119280.0,
      "end_time": 120730.0,
      "text": "And that, by the way, is why the work"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 120730.0,
      "end_time": 122964.0,
      "text": "that The Washington Post and other great newspapers"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 122964.0,
      "end_time": 124929.0,
      "text": "around the world do is so important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124930.0,
      "end_time": 127490.0,
      "text": "because they are often the ones doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 127490.0,
      "end_time": 130900.0,
      "text": "that initial scrutiny even before the government agencies do"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 130900.0,
      "end_time": 132591.0,
      "text": "But in a way the general sentiment towards"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 132591.0,
      "end_time": 136960.0,
      "text": "the big, innovative tech companies has changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 136960.0,
      "end_time": 141200.0,
      "text": "I mean, Facebook, Google, Apple, Amazon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 141200.0,
      "end_time": 144300.0,
      "text": "they used to be seen as the nice guys in T shirts"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 144300.0,
      "end_time": 146110.0,
      "text": "that are saving the world, and now they are"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 146110.0,
      "end_time": 149475.0,
      "text": "sometimes portrayed as the kind of evil of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 149475.0,
      "end_time": 154475.0,
      "text": "And the debate about the big four or the big five,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 154880.0,
      "end_time": 158900.0,
      "text": "if The Economist is suggesting a split up"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160840.0,
      "end_time": 164200.0,
      "text": "other powerful people like George Soros"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164200.0,
      "end_time": 165613.0,
      "text": "are giving speeches in Davos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166880.0,
      "end_time": 170760.0,
      "text": "the EU Commission is taking pretty tough positions here."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 170760.0,
      "end_time": 173700.0,
      "text": "Do you think that there is a change"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 173700.0,
      "end_time": 174430.0,
      "text": "in mindset in the society?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 174430.0,
      "end_time": 177780.0,
      "text": "And what should the big tech companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177780.0,
      "end_time": 180480.0,
      "text": "what should Amazon learn from that or do with that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180480.0,
      "end_time": 183900.0,
      "text": "I think, I do sense, I mean, I think again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 183900.0,
      "end_time": 184960.0,
      "text": "I think it's a natural instinct,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 184960.0,
      "end_time": 188800.0,
      "text": "I think we humans, especially in the Western world"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 188800.0,
      "end_time": 191750.0,
      "text": "and especially inside democracies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191750.0,
      "end_time": 197740.0,
      "text": "are wired to be skeptical and mindful of large institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 198180.0,
      "end_time": 200280.0,
      "text": "of any kind, we're skeptical, I'm sure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 200280.0,
      "end_time": 201580.0,
      "text": "we're skeptical of our government"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 201580.0,
      "end_time": 203960.0,
      "text": "always in the United States, state governments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 203960.0,
      "end_time": 207450.0,
      "text": "local governments, I assume it's similar in Germany."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 207450.0,
      "end_time": 210850.0,
      "text": "It's healthy, because they're big, powerful institutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210850.0,
      "end_time": 213160.0,
      "text": "You know, the police, the military, whatever it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 213160.0,
      "end_time": 214960.0,
      "text": "it doesn't mean that you don't trust them"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 214960.0,
      "end_time": 217881.0,
      "text": "or that they're bad or evil or anything like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 217881.0,
      "end_time": 221890.0,
      "text": "they're just, they have a lot of power and control"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 221890.0,
      "end_time": 223790.0,
      "text": "and so you want to inspect them."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 223790.0,
      "end_time": 224929.0,
      "text": "Maybe that's a better word."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 224930.0,
      "end_time": 227370.0,
      "text": "You kinda wanna always be inspecting them."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 227370.0,
      "end_time": 229617.0,
      "text": "And I think if you look at the big tech companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 229617.0,
      "end_time": 233899.0,
      "text": "they have gotten large enough that they need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 233900.0,
      "end_time": 235340.0,
      "text": "they're going to be inspected."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 235340.0,
      "end_time": 237710.0,
      "text": "And by the way, it's not personal."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 237710.0,
      "end_time": 240600.0,
      "text": "I think where some of the, where you can go astray on this"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 240600.0,
      "end_time": 243120.0,
      "text": "if you're the founder of a company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 243120.0,
      "end_time": 244270.0,
      "text": "one of these big tech companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 244270.0,
      "end_time": 248190.0,
      "text": "or any other big institution, if you go astray on this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 248190.0,
      "end_time": 249977.0,
      "text": "you might start to take it personally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 249977.0,
      "end_time": 252303.0,
      "text": "like what why are you inspecting me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 256588.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260803.00000000003,
      "text": "And I wish that people would just say yes, it's fine."
    }
  ]
}